Module kivakit.resource

Package com.telenav.kivakit.resource.resources.packaged

package com.telenav.kivakit.resource.resources.packaged
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    Packaged
    An object having a (KivaKit) Package.
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Package
    An abstraction for locating and copying Resources in Java packages.
    Package.Resolver
    Resolves package resource identifiers that are of the form "classpath:/a/b/c" into ResourceFolders (in the form of Packages).
    PackageResource
    A readable Resource in a package, as specified by PackagePath or ModuleResource (which has a ModuleReference and URI), and a name.
    PackageResource.Resolver
    Resolves ResourceIdentifiers of the form "classpath:/a/b/resource.txt" into Resources by creating a PackageResource for the identifier.
